Author: factcheckdotorg
Content: A baseless conspiracy theory claims that a secret supercomputer was used to switch votes from Donald Trump to Joe Biden. Experts — and the federal Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency — have said the theory is a hoax. https://t.co/UFz1fpDLr0

Author: snopes
Content: Trump’s legal allies have tried to argue that if poll workers weren’t on hand, anything could have happened out of their view. But they have not provided any evidence of nefarious activity. https://t.co/zJQAuqXrVF
